{"lastModified":1763380197360,"uri":"c::22607912615::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLuna 49 GOLD is a premium catamaran designed for ultimate comfort and privacy, offering exceptional amenities for an unforgettable charter experience. The yacht features:\n\nGuest Accommodations:\n\n4 spacious double cabins, each equipped with en-suite bathrooms, ensuring comfort and privacy for all guests.\nAir conditioning is available in every cabin and the saloon, providing a cool retreat even on the hottest days.\n\nCrew Facilities:\n\n2 single crew cabins located in the forward section of the yacht, along with a separate crew bathroom. This arrangement ensures the crew can provide seamless service without disturbing the privacy of the guests.\n\nAmenities and Equipment:\n\nFully equipped kitchen, including an ice maker and coffee machine, perfect for preparing gourmet meals and refreshing beverages.\nTwo refrigerators, one conveniently located in the cockpit for easy access.\nWater maker and generator, allowing the yacht to remain self-sufficient for a week without needing to dock.\nSmart home control system, enabling effortless management of onboard systems for lighting, sound, and more.\nHigh-quality sound system with three independent zones (bow, cockpit, and flybridge), all controlled via the saloon’s plotter or flybridge.\nComfortable outdoor cushions, creating inviting lounging spaces throughout the deck and flybridge.\nAdvanced rigging, including a full batten mainsail with a lazy bag, electric winches, and a furling and self-tacking system on the jib, all designed for effortless handling. All sail controls are conveniently managed from the flybridge, ensuring optimal comfort and efficiency while sailing.\n\nAdditional Features for Fun:\n\nComes equipped with a stand-up paddleboard (SUP) and snorkeling gear. Offers the possibility to include additional water toys such as kayaks, Seabobs, fishing rods, wakeboards, or inflatable towables, ensuring endless fun and adventure for guests.\n\nThe Luna 49 is designed to deliver an unparalleled charter experience, combining cutting-edge technology, elegant design, and thoughtful functionality for a memorable getaway on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"GOLD","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::e3e94610-3a3c-11f0-a4a8-1d57fd4d75fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e6fc4a0-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e93c760-3a3c-11f0-a9bd-d3d11e97551b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e941580-3a3c-11f0-a9bd-d3d11e97551b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e9219b0-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e7235a0-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e854870-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e9240c0-3a3c-11f0-a9bd-d3d11e97551b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e92b5f0-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e7c20b0-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e8a0360-3a3c-11f0-bea2-9b49b83438e7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0e968680-3a3c-11f0-9cbb-9f1c3f5ab8c4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::aebabc00-3a30-11f0-aeca-8d840c49cba3::assets::0